and the concept is important.

57
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,350
An inertial frame is a frame

58
00:03:24,350 --> 00:03:27,620
with respect to which 
the laws of Newton are valid,

59
00:03:27,620 --> 00:03:31,790
and the center of the inertial frame, 
which is orthogonal coordinate system,

60
00:03:31,790 --> 00:03:33,740
will depend on the application.

61
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:37,280
Now the validity of Newton's law 
is very general.

62
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:40,030
It's a very powerful set of laws,

63
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:42,830
the Apollo program, 
the International Space Station,

64
